# Upload filter for `gcloud builds submit`. MUST exclude .acceptance/ (holds the
# gitignored .env with the DeepSeek key + the target repo) so secrets never reach
# Cloud Build / GCS. Keep apps/ + skills/ + infra/ + manifests (the build needs them).
.git
.acceptance
.claude
docs
tasks
notes
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
*.png
*.log
.DS_Store
README.md
npmrc.recommended
